name: kubeaudit
description: Official kubeaudit image. Kubeaudit audits Kubernetes clusters for common security controls.
full_description:
Read more about Kubeaudit on Github: https://github.com/Shopify/kubeaudit

We release three tags for each image:
* latest: `shopify/kubeaudit:latest`
* minor versions (new features and breaking changes): eg. `shopify/kubeaudit:v0.11`
* patch versions (bug fixes): eg. `shopify/kubeaudit:v0.11.5`

See https://github.com/Shopify/kubeaudit/releases for the latest version.
